      <title>Starboard 斥资 10 亿美元入股辉瑞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-takes-1b-stake-in-pfizer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，激进投资者 Starboard Value 已入股辉瑞公司约 10 亿美元，并试图推动这家陷入困境的制药巨头扭亏为盈。彭博社的 Liana Baker 与 Katie Greifeld 一起在“彭博市场”节目中讨论这一问题。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/starboard-takes-1b-stake-in-pfizer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行前官员预计十月份将大幅降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/former-bank-of-canada-official-sees-jumbo-rate-cut-in-october</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行管理机构的一位前成员表示，官员应该在本月晚些时候将借贷成本降低半个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/former-bank-of-canada-official-sees-jumbo-rate-cut-in-october</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:06:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于循环信贷下降，美国消费者借贷增长放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-consumer-borrowing-growth-slows-on-drop-in-revolving-credit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[8 月份，美国消费者借贷增长速度低于一个月前，受到信用卡余额 2021 年 3 月以来最大降幅的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/us-consumer-borrowing-growth-slows-on-drop-in-revolving-credit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 19:05:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利央行对政府增长目标表示担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bank-of-italy-signals-concern-over-government-growth-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利央行对该国经济增长表示担忧，称今年该国经济扩张速度可能低于之前的预期，这使得政府更难实现其目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bank-of-italy-signals-concern-over-government-growth-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:44:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Roundhill Investments 首席执行官谈中国龙 ETF (DRAG)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/roundhill-investments-ceo-on-china-dragons-etf-drag-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Roundhill Investments 首席执行官 Dave Mazza 讨论了 Roundhill China Dragons ETF (DRAG)，并表示其背后的想法是捕捉美国七大豪强所代表的同一类型的公司，但针对的是中国股市。他在“ETF IQ”节目中与 Scarlet Fu、Katie Greifeld 和 Eric Balchunas 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/roundhill-investments-ceo-on-china-dragons-etf-drag-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:21:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟贷款部门提议通过 IPO 投资促进市场联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-lending-arm-proposes-ipo-investments-to-foster-markets-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟贷款机构正在制定计划，促进欧盟境内企业上市，这是降低资本壁垒和提高竞争力的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-lending-arm-proposes-ipo-investments-to-foster-markets-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德的 Akullian 看到了大盘股价值的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/blackrock-s-akullian-sees-opportunity-in-large-cap-value</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德 iShares 投资策略美洲区主管 Kristy Akullian 表示，现在是从超大盘股转向大盘股的时候，而不是从大盘股转向小盘股的时候。她还在“ETF IQ”节目中与 Katie Greifeld、Scarlet Fu 和 Eric Balchunas 讨论了 iShares MSCI USA Quality GARP ETF 和固定收益。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-07/blackrock-s-akullian-sees-opportunity-in-large-cap-value</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 17:58:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ishbia 旗下 Shore Capital 为三支基金募集 19 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ishbia-s-shore-capital-raises-1-9-billion-for-three-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shore Capital Partners 是一家总部位于芝加哥的私募股权公司，由贾斯汀·伊什比亚 (Justin Ishbia) 领导，该公司已完成对三只新基金的募资，募资总额达 19 亿美元，其中两只基金将专注于拓展公司传统的小企业投资领域以外的业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/ishbia-s-shore-capital-raises-1-9-billion-for-three-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 14:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alphabet 股价下跌，科技巨头股价暴跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球一些最大科技公司的抛售导致股市跌至盘中低点，延续了此前受地缘政治焦虑和美联储下个月将选择小幅降息推动的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-after-us-jobs-report-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:37:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争风险令投资者紧张不安，布伦特原油飙升至每桶 80 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东局势愈发紧张，引发人们对以色列可能袭击伊朗石油基础设施的猜测，布伦特原油价格飙升至每桶 80 美元以上，创下 8 月份以来的最高价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
